  "text": "In the twenty-first century, malignancies are the second leading cause of death after cardiovascular disease in developed countries and show a slight upward trend. During chemotherapy, cyclophosphamide is an effective immunosuppressive drug with wide application field, e.g. haematologic malignancies and in each type of solid tumours, etc. [CITATION_1] . It is the reason that appeared on the most important drugs' list published by WHO in April, 2015 [2] . It is a good tool during polyneuropathy treatment, but in several cases, it can induct this disorder too [CITATION_2] .",
